    "body" : "<p>it results from the standard representation of signed values as binary numbers. For a full description see <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two%27s_complement\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two%27s_complement</a>.</p>\n\n<p>-Rich </p>\n"
